headline: Dover Announces Fourth Quarter 2025 Earnings Release Date, Conference Call and Webcast
summary: Dover (NYSE: DOV) announced today that it will release fourth quarter 2025 earnings at approximately 6:00 a.m. Central time (7:00 a.m. Eastern time) on Thursday, January 29, 2026. Later that morning, Dover will host a conference call at 11:00 a.m. Central time (12:00 p.m. Eastern time) to discuss these results.
